30:20.066 --> 30:23.603
Ok, Morgan, get a shot
of the whole thing!

30:23.637 --> 30:25.106
Ok.

30:27.573 --> 30:29.275
We're missing something.

30:29.309 --> 30:31.145
Someone sent us here
for a reason.

30:31.178 --> 30:33.280
Yeah! To fuck with us!

30:33.313 --> 30:35.082
No. 'Cause then it'll be over.

30:35.114 --> 30:37.083
