30:39.119 --> 30:40.388
Ok.

30:40.420 --> 30:42.088
Gross.

30:42.121 --> 30:44.292
Wait.
What?

30:46.726 --> 30:48.195
What is it?

30:48.227 --> 30:51.164
It's another USB key.

30:51.198 --> 30:55.136
-Ok. Let's go!
-Ok.

31:32.840 --> 31:35.810
So, let's see this USB key.

31:35.842 --> 31:38.245
Why? It's just a USB.

31:38.277 --> 31:40.647
Can I just see it?

31:45.486 --> 31:46.853
What the hell?

31:46.887 --> 31:48.656
It's one of the "scanny"
thingies.

31:48.688 --> 31:51.859
-My phone can't do that.
-Yeah, me neither.

31:51.891 --> 31:52.927
John's can.

31:52.959 --> 31:55.129
When we get to the water park,
he can scan this.

32:04.871 --> 32:09.209
Are you kidding me?
Jesus! Yes!

32:09.243 --> 32:12.679
Damn! That's nice!
That's serious.

32:13.913 --> 32:16.150
All right, ladies.
A little too young.

32:25.492 --> 32:28.295
There he is! Rhys!

32:28.328 --> 32:30.598
What the hell is he doing?

32:30.630 --> 32:33.234
That's right.

32:33.266 --> 32:35.268
