You guys made it.

32:37.336 --> 32:38.638
John's at the Bowl.

32:38.671 --> 32:40.240
Should we go?

32:40.274 --> 32:44.611
Yes! Let's go!

32:44.644 --> 32:46.346
Take this.

32:46.380 --> 32:49.183
Yeah, yeah! This too.

32:49.216 --> 32:51.318
Here take it! Take it!
Take it!

32:54.388 --> 32:55.890
When you're free
we'll need your phone.

32:55.922 --> 32:59.292
-Sorry, I'll be off in 15.
-15, great! I love you.

32:59.325 --> 33:00.193
Hey! What are you doing?

33:02.329 --> 33:05.299
Holy shit!

33:05.332 --> 33:10.737
Wow!

33:10.771 --> 33:14.408
God! I can't breathe!

33:21.848 --> 33:24.452
I'm fucking dying.
I'm fucking dying.

33:26.320 --> 33:28.156
Yes!

33:30.323 --> 33:32.226
Did you catch that shit?

33:35.329 --> 33:37.698
Hey, I think she just stole
that chair.

33:43.303 --> 33:45.305
I think you could
probably be a model.

33:45.339 --> 33:47.675
No shit.

33:47.707 --> 33:49.810
-Hey!
-Hey, John!

33:49.842 --> 33:53.279
-Smile for the camera, bitch.
-What's up?

33:53.313 --> 33:54.415
Check it out.

33:54.448 --> 33:56.717
-Sweet. What is it?
-It's a QR card.

33:56.749 --> 33:58.952
What? This is crazy!

33:58.986 --> 34:01.354
He took the time to make this
look like a USB key.

34:01.388 --> 34:02.856
We don't know if it's a he?

34:02.889 --> 34:04.725
Why? You think a girl did this?

34:04.757 --> 34:07.294
Hey, girls can be just
as sick as guys.

34:07.326 --> 34:08.996
Yeah, no shit!

34:09.027 --> 34:11.797
-Yeah.
-"First Blood"?

34:11.831 --> 34:15.202
-The Rambo movie?
-Ok.

34:16.402 --> 34:17.771
What is that?

34:17.803 --> 34:20.239
Is that a finger?
That's a finger.

34:20.273 --> 34:21.808
Fucking looks real, man.

34:21.842 --> 34:26.380
-What's it in?
-In a chess case?

34:26.411 --> 34:27.213
Maybe it's a link.

34:27.246 --> 34:30.717
Hum. Website
for the Northside Mall.

34:32.418 --> 34:34.420
-What time does the mall close?
-Really? Seriously, guys?

35:03.749 --> 35:06.519
Very much.
I would appreciate it.

35:08.689 --> 35:12.393
No, no, no,
I can't wait until...

35:12.425 --> 35:15.295
No, no, I really need to
get out tonight.

35:15.329 --> 35:17.997
It has to be tonight.

35:18.030 --> 35:21.367
No, I get
where you're coming from,

35:21.401 --> 35:22.903
I understand, I do...

35:22.936 --> 35:25.673
Look, we just had a death
in the family

35:25.706 --> 35:27.675
and I really need
to get out tonight.

35:27.707 --> 35:31.445
It's imperative
that I get out tonight, please.

35:31.477 --> 35:33.947
I just...
Whatever you can find.

35:43.423 --> 35:46.392
So text us
if you find anything?

35:46.425 --> 35:48.394
Yes, ma'am!

35:48.427 --> 35:49.696
And if anything weird happens.

35:49.729 --> 35:51.564
Ok, so go ahead
and define "weird"

35:51.597 --> 35:53.333
under these circumstances.

35:53.367 --> 35:55.436
Do we even know
what we're looking for?

35:55.468 --> 36:00.506
Anything out of the ordinary,
like... a finger in a VHS case.

36:00.539 --> 36:04.410
Right. Ok.

36:04.443 --> 36:06.512
So what's going on
with you and Kate?

36:06.546 --> 36:08.982
I don't know, man. I've
been asking myself that too.

36:09.014 --> 36:10.717
You fuck her or what?

36:10.751 --> 36:12.619
No, that's the problem.

36:12.651 --> 36:14.921
Man, you have a reputation
at stake here, don't you?

36:14.954 --> 36:16.155
What are you talking about?

36:16.189 --> 36:18.425
Dude! She's gonna be watching
this footage, you know that?

36:18.457 --> 36:20.794
Yeah! Sorry, Kate,
I'm just kidding. We love you!

36:22.628 --> 36:25.131
I guess it would help if we knew
what we were looking for.

36:25.164 --> 36:26.933
VHS should be in the back.

36:29.403 --> 36:31.405
Excuse me.
Sorry.

36:31.438 --> 36:34.874
Excuse me! See?
VHS clearance sale.

36:37.811 --> 36:39.613
Take this side.
I'll take this side.

36:39.646 --> 36:41.548
Awesome!

36:41.581 --> 36:44.985
<i>Blood and Sweat. Eat Dirt.
Awesome.</i>

36:45.017 --> 36:47.553
Don't just toss them aside.
We might miss something.

36:47.586 --> 36:49.489
Especially because we know
what we're looking for.

36:49.523 --> 36:51.091
Holy shit!
What?

36:51.124 --> 36:54.495
<i>Holy shit! Dude, Devilution 9.</i>

36:54.528 --> 36:57.097
What? I thought
there were only 8.

36:57.130 --> 37:00.099
There were.
That's gotta be fake, for sure.

37:00.133 --> 37:02.903
Shit, dude!
We're on the back of that!

37:02.936 --> 37:04.537
What?

37:04.570 --> 37:05.773
Open it!

37:05.805 --> 37:08.141
Not in here.

37:08.175 --> 37:09.743
You're gonna buy it?

37:09.776 --> 37:11.645
Can I even buy this?

37:11.677 --> 37:14.013
We have to take this.

37:14.046 --> 37:16.483
Fuck that! You can take it,
expert criminal.

37:16.515 --> 37:18.452
I can't. It will be
a 3rd strike for me.

37:18.485 --> 37:20.586
I'm not doing it.

37:20.619 --> 37:23.456
Man, we need this.
I can't do it. Just take it.

37:23.490 --> 37:26.494
-He's standing right there.
-Give me that!

37:28.461 --> 37:30.496
We're just customers.
We're not doing anything wrong.

37:30.530 --> 37:33.167
Take the damn thing!
Put it in your bag right now.

37:33.200 --> 37:36.203
You fucking owe me!
You fucking owe me!

37:36.235 --> 37:37.537
Jesus, John!

37:41.006 --> 37:42.610
Act cool! Act cool!

37:55.622 --> 37:57.457
Hey! Just in time.
We found it.

37:58.657 --> 38:01.661
<i>-Devilution 9?
-There is no Devolution 9.</i>

38:01.695 --> 38:03.597
What makes you so sure
that it's from him?

38:03.630 --> 38:08.901
Look! Do you see that?
That is us!

38:08.934 --> 38:10.503
You've got to be
pretty fucking close

38:10.537 --> 38:12.573
to get a picture like that.

38:12.606 --> 38:15.776
Do you understand the amount
of time and effort

38:15.809 --> 38:18.144
it even takes
to make something like this?

38:18.177 --> 38:20.179
This guy's not fucking around.

38:20.213 --> 38:22.649
We need to stop giving
this guy what he wants!

38:22.682 --> 38:23.950
How about we see
what's on the tape?

38:23.983 --> 38:25.452
It's here. Let's just do it.

38:28.622 --> 38:30.491
Ok. Here we go.

38:46.273 --> 38:47.575
<i>Look at you.</i>

38:49.709 --> 38:52.546
<i>Ok. Hi there!</i>

38:54.213 --> 38:56.249
<i>You're feeling those drugs?</i>

39:01.121 --> 39:03.557
<i>Yeah, I think so.</i>

39:07.626 --> 39:09.662
<i>Yeah, I think so.</i>

39:12.064 --> 39:14.267
<i>Now, this shouldn't hurt
too much.</i>

39:16.669 --> 39:17.771
<i>It's for your own good.</i>

39:17.803 --> 39:20.573
God! God!

39:24.577 --> 39:26.514
No!

39:30.950 --> 39:33.719
<i>Aaaah!</i>

40:35.081 --> 40:37.950
Ok. No, no, no, no.
No way, that was real.

40:37.983 --> 40:39.151
There's no way that was real.

40:39.184 --> 40:41.087
I don't know, man.
It looks pretty real.

40:41.121 --> 40:43.389
Why can't we go to the cops?

40:43.423 --> 40:45.258
The worse that can happen is
that this is fake

40:45.291 --> 40:47.727
and we look like idiots
but at least it'll be over.

40:47.760 --> 40:49.095
I don't know what to do.

40:49.128 --> 40:51.097
I don't want to get
my dad involved.

40:51.131 --> 40:53.767
This is obviously just
a game to him, right?

40:55.334 --> 40:58.137
Ok. So let's say we do go
to the cops, then what?

40:58.171 --> 41:00.807
I just know that getting
the cops involved is a bad idea.

41:00.840 --> 41:03.376
He's gonna fucking kill us,
girl, if we go to the cops!

41:03.410 --> 41:06.913
Guys, you should be
holding hands.

41:06.945 --> 41:10.316
Guys, I have a feeling
that this is over.

41:10.349 --> 41:14.954
We've no more leads.
What else could possibly happen?

41:17.289 --> 41:19.892
You couldn't really tell where
the girl was in that video.

41:19.925 --> 41:22.361
It looked underground.
No windows or anything.

41:22.394 --> 41:24.030
Yeah, maybe.

41:24.064 --> 41:26.233
I'm going inside.
Are you guys coming?

41:26.265 --> 41:28.267
-Yeah.
-No, I gotta get home.

41:30.836 --> 41:34.974
-Ok. Well... I'll see you.
-Ok.

41:36.776 --> 41:38.712
Wow.

41:40.213 --> 41:43.717
-Just... not now, ok?
-Why not?

41:43.749 --> 41:45.851
Just not now!

41:45.885 --> 41:48.689
-Ok. Never, right?
-Don't be a jerk.

41:48.722 --> 41:50.990
You're the one
jerking me around.

41:51.023 --> 41:53.759
John... just don't...

41:53.793 --> 41:55.729
What the hell is the matter
with you?

41:58.831 --> 42:00.800
I'll see you.

42:00.834 --> 42:02.869
Will you stop filming this!

42:02.901 --> 42:04.804
Jesus Christ!

42:12.878 --> 42:15.314
-I'm sorry, Kate.
-It's ok.

42:15.347 --> 42:18.418
It's not his fault. I'm
just messed up from all of it.

42:18.450 --> 42:20.186
It's pretty fucked up.

42:20.220 --> 42:23.790
I'm not going to the cops
though 'cause it's fake.

42:23.822 --> 42:27.193
I'm sure it's one of John's exes
trying to fuck with him.

42:27.227 --> 42:29.162
Or get revenge on me.

42:31.331 --> 42:34.735
-It's not a bad theory.
-You hadn't thought of that yet?

42:34.767 --> 42:37.737
I thought you were the one in
all those conspiracy theories.

42:37.771 --> 42:41.173
Yeah, but Kate, this is
seriously like fucked up.

42:41.206 --> 42:43.275
I think the girl in the video
is actually in trouble.

42:43.309 --> 42:44.778
Morgan, it's fake!

42:44.811 --> 42:47.213
Ok, but have you seen Diane
lately?

42:47.247 --> 42:48.782
She's been gone for 2 days.

42:48.814 --> 42:50.818
