you saw her?

42:52.952 --> 42:55.188
Like... 2 days ago.

42:55.220 --> 42:58.958
She came in here and asked us
if we needed anything.

43:03.930 --> 43:05.398
Voicemail.

43:05.430 --> 43:07.166
Hey, Diane, it's Kate.

43:07.200 --> 43:09.803
Just checking in. We haven't
seen you in a couple of days.

43:09.836 --> 43:11.872
Give us a call. Bye!

43:13.273 --> 43:14.841
You don't think she has
something to do

43:14.874 --> 43:17.910
with all this weird shit
going on.

43:17.943 --> 43:20.380
Get over your theories.

43:20.412 --> 43:22.515
I'm going to bed.

43:25.318 --> 43:27.121
Don't wake me up
